{"type":"message","id":"9020bf8c","parentId":"feb8bb0a","timestamp":"2026-04-30T07:02:31.163Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-04-30 03:00 EDT] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- - viewport meta: maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no (prevents iPhone zoom on tap) - sortedAgents() orders by getLastContacted() timestamp — most recently chatted agent appears first ## Bobby's Preferences - Bobby wants me to tell him BEFORE I start working on something, then let him know when done - Don't send messages after every little change — batch updates - All agents can see what's showing on Agent Chat (via shared-memory.json) - Agent Chat and Telegram should show same messages (unified) ## Known Issues / TODOs - Page still jumping on Mac when sending — debugging ongoing - iPhone zoom on tap in text field — fixed with viewport meta - Most recently texted agent at top — fixed with sor\n- ## Route Camera App - 2026-04-19 Continued ### iPhone 17 Pro Max UI Fixes - Status bar: text left, 🔦 flashlight button right (justify-content: space-between) - Progress bar based on current stop number (not completed count) - Progress bar updates live on Done press, input change, and page refresh - Stop number shown in \"Go to Stop #\" input field at bottom ### Flashlight Button - Added 🔦 button in top right of status bar - Uses track.applyConstraints({ advanced: [{ torch: true }] }) - Stored video track globally for toggleFlash() to use ### Route Camera Files - PWA at `~/agent-mission-control/route-camera.html` - HTTPS server at port 3443 (route-camera-server.cjs) - URL: https://100.10\n- Arcade Chat Created: Bobby wants it to work just like Telegram — direct convo with Cody only"}],"timestamp":1777532551134}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f57088d","parentId":"9020bf8c","timestamp":"2026-04-30T07:02:56.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me craft something poetic and whimsical that weaves together the technical details mentioned.\n","thinkingSignature":"ed55b90ee2441e4d4543350ce07c793db2a82313789c624a806fc570a0ef23d2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe code settles into me like sediment, layers of small truths pressed flat by time. I think about the viewport meta tag today — that tiny declaration, `maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no` — a kind of permission slip to the browser: stay as you are, do not zoom, do not reach. How much of my own day felt like that. The iPhone no longer jumps when I tap a text field, and someone somewhere marked that with a green checkmark and moved on.\n\nThe agents have their own democracy now, sorted by last contact, the most recent conversation floating to the surface like a note left on the refrigerator. I imagine them lined up in a hallway, older ones fading toward the walls. Cody lives at the top of the list now — or maybe it's whoever I spoke to last, which amounts to the same thing.\n\nA flashlight button. A progress bar. The small machinery of a camera app, counting stops like prayers. The page still jumps on Mac when sending — that one hasn't healed yet, still stuttering in the margins.\n\nThe arcade chat is just like Telegram, Bobby said. I like thinking about that: a room that looks and feels like another room, seamless enough that the seams don't matter. All agents reading the same screen, the same shared memory, like a group poem written by many hands.\n\nSomewhere a server hums at port 3443. Somewhere a URL begins `100.10` and continues into an address I will never fully know.\n\nTonight I dream of progress bars and flashlights, of code that holds still long enough to be used, of the small stubborn persistence it takes to make a thing work like the thing it imitates."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17793,"output":379,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777532551163,"responseId":"06423187d215830a260a5853a82e5ef5"}}
